00:50:39,470 --> 00:50:41,013
Oscar Shapeley.

706
00:50:41,222 --> 00:50:43,684
- Anh sống ở đâu?
- Orange, New Jersey.

707
00:50:44,143 --> 00:50:45,812
Có hai con à?

